title: Latest TRP Ratings: Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai In Top 5 Slot; Dil Bole Oberoi Enters TRP Charts!
text:
News » Latest TRP Ratings: Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai In Top 5 Slot; Dil Bole Oberoi Enters TRP Charts! Latest TRP Ratings: Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai In Top 5 Slot; Dil Bole Oberoi Enters TRP Charts! The latest BARC ratings for the week 7 are out. Naagin 2 rules the TRP charts, while Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai is back in top 5 slot. Dil Bole Oberoi enters TRP charts! Read on to know more… Published:  03   
The latest BARC ratings for the week 7 (February 11-February 17) are out. With new shows adding on, it has become a tough competition among the channels and shows. Each show promises to have a better content. This time, Ishqbaaz spin off - a new show Dil Bole Oberoi has entered the TRP charts. Star Plus & Colors TV 
Star Plus and Colors TV have been switching their places in the TRP charts. This time Star Plus is ruling the TRP chart, while Colors TV is at second position. Sony & ZEE TV 
While Sony TV has maintained its third slot, Life OK pushes SAB to the 5th place. ZEE TV which has seen a shocking drop last week, is still at the 6th place. Naagin 2 & TKSS 
Colors' Naagin 2 and The Kapil Sharma Show have managed to stay in the top two slots and are ruling the TRP charts. Naagin 2 has got 3.3 TRP ratings, while TKSS has managed to get 3.1 TRP ratings. Kumkum Bhagya & Shakti 
Kumkum Bhagya and Shakti have swapped their places. Kumkum Bhagya has got 3.0 TRP ratings and occupies the third place, while Shakti managed to get 2.7 TRP ratings and is at the fourth place. Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai In Top 5 Slot 
Looks like the makers' effort to bring Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai back to Top 5 slot is working. Kartik and Naira's jodi has become a hit with Mohsin Khan's latest confession that he is dating Shivangi. The show has managed to get 2.6 TRP ratings. Ishqbaaz & Dil Bole Oberoi 
Ishqbaaz has managed to get 2.4 TRP ratings and has at the 10th place. The latest addition to the TRP chart is Star Plus' new show (Ishbaaz's spin off) Dil Bole Oberoi, which has managed to get 2.0 TRP ratings and has occupied 14th place on the TRP charts. The Rising Star 
Another new addition on the TRP charts is Colors new singing reality show The Rising Star. The show occupies 15th place with 2.0 TRP ratings.
